        "subject": "LU-2641 ldiskfs: update quota API",
        "message": "LU-2641 ldiskfs: update quota API\n\nCommit 871a2931 renamed vfs_dq_init to dquot_initialize. (v2.6.34)\nCommit 9f754758 renamed vfs_dq_drop to dquot_drop. (v2.6.34)\nCommit b43fa828 renamed vfs_dq_transfer to dquot_transfer. (v2.6.34)\nCommit 0f0dd62f killed vfs_dq_off and vfs_dq_quota_on_remount and\nreplaced\nthem with dquot_suspend and dquot_resume. (v2.6.34)\n\nCommit b9b2dd36 modified ->get_dqblk to use struct fs_disk_quota.\n(v2.6.34)\nCommit c472b432 modified ->set_dqblk to use struct fs_disk_quota.\n(v2.6.34)\n\nCommit 5fb324ad added a wait argument to ->quota_sync. (v2.6.33)\nCommit ceed1723 removed the wait argument again. (v3.5)\n\nSigned-off-by: Jeff Mahoney <jeffm@suse.com>\nChange-Id: I61d74e6d280f27b9d2a71c20468bf4ab4591f61a\n"
